{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Rofa8rKVZa33hWmqefNJ4t","type":"tool_result","content":"  2680в†’| # | Action | Priority | Owner | Status |\n  2681в†’|---|--------|----------|-------|--------|\n  2682в†’| 1 | **Fix `parseRalphMessage()` to skip JSON lines** вЂ” if line starts with `{`, skip regex matching entirely and let stream-json parser handle it. | CRITICAL | Dev | OPEN вЂ” **this is the root cause fix** |\n  2683в†’| 2 | **Make `updateStoryStatus()` defensive** вЂ” reject unknown story keys instead of creating new entries via `?? defaultStoryState()`. Log a warning and return early. | CRITICAL | Dev | OPEN |\n  2684в†’| 3 | **Add circuit breaker for repeated identical state fixes** вЂ” detect N identical corrections within M sessions and halt ralph with an error. | HIGH | Dev | OPEN вЂ” carried from session 15 |\n  2685в†’| 4 | **Add ralph sprint-complete termination** вЂ” refuse to launch sessions when `sprint.done === sprint.total`. | HIGH | Dev | OPEN вЂ” carried from session 9 |\n  2686в†’| 5 | **Clean up cost data** вЂ” remove phantom story entries from tracking to get accurate per-story costs. | MEDIUM | Tooling | OPEN |\n  2687в†’| 6 | **Convert action items 1-4 to sprint 2 stories** вЂ” these must be the first stories in the next sprint. | HIGH | PM | OPEN вЂ” carried from session 13 |\n  2688в†’| 7 | **Reduce \"unknown\" story cost bucket** вЂ” $135.26 (20.8%) unattributed. | LOW | Tooling | OPEN вЂ” carried forward |\n  2689в†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Qcu6hf3g4YB7b8H7MEmcGR","session_id":"2a44c687-0795-47af-a7f4-46576056f827","uuid":"47c9ca89-b30c-4a14-a223-a533223b9552","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:17:16.090Z"}
